<h1 class="article-title entry-title" itemprop='headline'>
	Leave work at work: How to properly end your day</h1>				<div class="article-featured-image">
				<img src="http://cdn1.tnwcdn.com/assets/images/transparent.png" data-src="http://cdn1.tnwcdn.com/wp-content/blogs.dir/1/files/2014/04/exit-sign-786x305.jpg" width="786" height="305" title="Leave work at work: How to properly end your day" alt="exit sign" class="lazy" />
			<noscript><img src="http://cdn1.tnwcdn.com/wp-content/blogs.dir/1/files/2014/04/exit-sign-786x305.jpg" width="786" height="305" title="Leave work at work: How to properly end your day" alt="exit sign" class="lazy" /></noscript>				</div>
